local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

state.unicode: These battles can also be played as multiplayer battles.|| You can access these through the multiplayer menu. || Each battle won here opens a path to the next one. || You are awarded a battle honour for each battle you win. || Your performance in battle determines what level of battle honour you receive. || Once you have finished a battle, you can replay it to try and achieve the highest honour available.

state.unicode: The Battle of Arcole was a bold attempt by Napoleon to outflank the Austrian army under General Alvinczy and cut its line of retreat before it could lift the siege of Mantua. The bridge crossing the Alpone was key to the battle and where Napoleon was famously seen caring the Tricolour.

uientry.unicode: You can increase or decrease battle difficulty with the slider.
